imdb.plot outline: This is about three artificial states which are, Kasik, Panturat and Tanta. All of them was neighbors but they felt feared to each other. Kasik was located at the northern. With the coldest weather, people could not grow any plants but it was rich of gems and diamonds. Panturat is good to grow crops as well as easy to connect with the city. Tanta is located near the ocean so the weather was always hot during through years.
